name: The Last Buffalo
description:
Third place (Collage category) The Giphoscope Award, 2014.
Produced frame by frame with Adobe Fireworks, cut one by one from Muybridge's Buffalo and Galloping Horse sequences on wikimedia commons and placed on a moving old west background stage.
